    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large spatulas used to break up the curd for cheesemaking. For knives with a curved blade used to cut and serve cheese, use "cheese knives (serving utensils)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
